---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="WordStash: Your Personal Vocabulary Companion - Madhu's Dream">
  <div class="pt-16 min-h-screen">
    <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium mb-8 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" />
          </svg>
          Back to Blog
        </a>
      </div>

      <header class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 text-white rounded-full text-sm font-medium">
            iOS Development
          </span>
          <time class="text-gray-600">February 28, 2026</time>
          <span class="text-gray-500">• 8 min read</span>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
          WordStash: Your Personal Vocabulary Companion
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Building a dead-simple iOS app for capturing and learning new words. From idea to App Store in one day.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="mb-12 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
        <img 
          src="/wordstash/image1.png" 
          alt="WordStash App"
          class="w-full"
          onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<div class=\'aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-cyan-100 flex items-center justify-center text-6xl\'>📚</div>'"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 mb-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">The Problem I Wanted to Solve</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            You know that moment when you're reading on your phone and come across a word you don't know? 
            You could switch apps, look it up, maybe save it somewhere... but honestly, it's too much friction. 
            By the time you get back to reading, you've lost your flow.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            I wanted something faster. <strong>Something that just works.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8 border border-blue-200">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">How It Works</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            WordStash is built around one simple idea: <strong>capturing words should take seconds, not minutes.</strong>
          </p>
          <ol class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-3 ml-6">
            <li class="font-medium">📖 See a new word while reading</li>
            <li class="font-medium">📋 Copy it</li>
            <li class="font-medium">📱 Open WordStash and tap the clipboard button</li>
            <li class="font-medium">✅ Done.</li>
          </ol>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            The app automatically fetches the meaning and usage examples using AI. No typing, no searching – just instant knowledge.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 mb-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Features I'm Proud Of</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
                🤖
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">AI-Powered Definitions</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                  Every word you add gets an automatic definition and real-world usage examples using OpenAI's API.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-cyan-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
                🔊
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Pronunciation Made Easy</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                  Tap the speaker icon next to any word and hear how it's pronounced. Works offline using iOS's built-in text-to-speech.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
                📇
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Flash Cards for Review</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                  Swipeable flash cards with smooth flip animations. Filter to review just your starred words.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
                ☁️
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Cloud Sync</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                  Your vocabulary syncs across all your devices using Supabase. iPhone to iPad – everything stays in sync.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 rounded-2xl p-10 text-white mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Built During My Hospital Stay</h2>
          <p class="text-white/90 text-lg">
            This app was created in just <strong>1 day</strong> during my 5-day hospital stay, using AI-driven development. 
            It's a testament to what's possible when you combine clear vision with modern development tools.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 mb-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">The Tech Stack</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
            {['SwiftUI', 'SwiftData', 'Supabase', 'OpenAI API', 'AVSpeechSynthesizer', 'iOS 17'].map(tech => (
              <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-center text-sm font-medium text-blue-900">
                {tech}
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 flex justify-between">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" />
          </svg>
          Back to Blog
        </a>
        <a href="/apps/wordstash" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium transition-colors">
          View App Details
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</Layout>
